lank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"3de347934b21c3c4ae2e2b1d6e3c64f9a6c5d364","tid":1777614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a6190cdddb8166e18e9db209c11c70c40f05cf3","tid":1777614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"056186e0e22827e8b83766f1027b4c62de36a0a2","tid":1777614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"香港80萬人12.8繼續「反共抗暴」大遊行 這一幕的光海之夜相信最能感動人（罕有高清實錄）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QABN7Y9nC_Q&amp;list=WL&amp;index=2&amp;t=50s&amp;ab_channel=%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQABN7Y9nC_Q%26list%3DWL%26index%3D2%26t%3D50s%26ab_channel%3D%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=b8c5b8be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QABN7Y9nC_Q&amp;list=WL&amp;index=2&amp;t=50s&amp;ab_channel=%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"你看見了什麽 ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"我看見了齊心<br />\n<br />\n我看見了堅持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZND72Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZND72Z.jpg&h=2eddc950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yH3WUH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyH3WUH1.jpg&h=b72b29b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://n